<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Product Page</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/product.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="product-section">
            <img src="~/image/air-purifier.jpg" alt="Product Image" class="product-image">
            <div class="product-info">
                <div class="product-description">
                    <h1>Pureair Pro</h1>
                    <div class="benefits-description">
                        <ul>
                            <li> Filtration System: HEPA, activated carbon, pre-filters.</li>
                            <li> Room Coverage: Up to 500 square feet.</li>
                            <li> CADR (Clean Air Delivery Rate): 300 cubic feet per minute (CFM).</li>
                            <li>Power Consumption: 30 watts.</li>
                            <li> Warranty: 1-year limited warranty.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="action-section">
                    <div class="discount-offer">
                        <h2>Special Discount Offer</h2>
                        <p>Get 10% off on your first purchase! Limited time offer.</p>
                    </div>
                    <button class="buy-button">Buy Now</button>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="benefits-section">
            <h2 class="benefits-title">Key Features of PureAir Pro</h2>
            <div class="benefits-content">
                <img src="~/image/airnew1.jpg" alt="Air Purifier Benefits" class="benefits-image">
                <div class="benefits-description">
                    <ul>
                        <li> Advanced Filtration: Equipped with a multi-stage filtration system, including HEPA, activated carbon, and pre-filters, the PureAir Pro effectively removes 99.97% of airborne contaminants, including dust, pollen, pet dander, smoke, and odors.</li>
                        <li> Smart Sensor Technology: The built-in smart sensors continuously monitor air quality and automatically adjust fan speed to maintain optimal indoor air quality levels.</li>
                        <li>Whisper-Quiet Operation: With ultra-quiet operation, the PureAir Pro purifies the air without disrupting your peace and quiet, making it ideal for use in bedrooms, living rooms, and offices.</li>
                        <li> Easy to Use: With intuitive controls and a user-friendly interface, the PureAir Pro is easy to operate and maintain, ensuring hassle-free operation.</li>
                        <li>Sleek and Modern Design: Featuring a sleek and modern design, the PureAir Pro complements any home or office decor, while its compact size allows for placement in any room.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
